{"id":232594877,"title":"有多少人持續帶著環保餐具的？","content":"前陣子自備環保吸管、餐具好像變成一股風潮\r\n但漸漸地看著身邊的朋友好像又開始用店家提供的免洗餐具…就覺得是不是這件事情又漸漸被淡忘了😣😣\r\n喝飲料如喝水的我\r\n之前也是跟風買了玻璃的環保吸管\r\n但很多其實都是平口通常根本插不進飲料封膜，再加上有的時候擔心亂放會碎掉就索性不帶😭\r\n後來看到這個crosspace的鈦吸管，覺得造型蠻美的又有斜口設計，收納的袋子也感覺很透氣\r\n都會乖乖的把它放包包\nhttps://i.imgur.com/GK7ypT0.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/EgZcN7O.jpg\n\r\n如果當天想喝飲料卻忘記帶吸管 也會懲罰自己不准喝飲料😱😱😱\r\n為了喝飲料~\r\n現在出門的口訣已經變成手機錢包鑰匙吸管了XD\r\n還有多少同學有在自備環保餐具的呢?","excerpt":"前陣子自備環保吸管、餐具好像變成一股風潮，但漸漸地看著身邊的朋友好像又開始用店家提供的免洗餐具…就覺得是不是這件事情又漸漸被淡忘了，喝飲料如喝水的我，之前也是跟風買了玻璃的環保吸管，但很多其實都是平口","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-29T10:24:50.571Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-29T12:23:36.055Z","commentCount":119,"likeCount":972,"tags":[],"topics":["無痕飲食","吸管"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"國立臺中科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":970},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/GK7ypT0.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/EgZcN7O.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"e86a5613-b860-422a-bb1a-bd54c4210eb5","url":"https://i.imgur.com/GK7ypT0l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/GK7ypT0l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/GK7ypT0l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-29T10:24:50.571Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-29T12:23:36.055Z"},{"id":"e86a5613-b860-422a-bb1a-bd54c4210eb5","url":"https://i.imgur.com/GK7ypT0.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/GK7ypT0","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/GK7ypT0l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-29T10:24:50.571Z","updatedAt":